0494|*HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Console\<path>S
S   |                           <    >
0495|*where <path> is the path of Survo on the disk.
S   |       <    >
0496|*Then the problem is resolved by deleting this key from the registry
0497|*by the REGEDIT program, for example.
